d2bba42ccc88487b5","tid":1164551,"uid":47905,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T12:09:36.000Z","msg":"他的太太雷切爾（Rachel）、蘭伯特6名兄弟及姊姊均希望終止治療，但他那虔誠天主教徒父母及另外兩名手足，就堅持蘭伯特應該活下去。<br />\n<br />\n真心覺得係呢對父母自私"},{"pid":"7e4bc0e3c2e4673310618f873fb4c0ad9da6c22a","tid":1164551,"uid":114275,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T12:32:12.000Z","msg":"佢老母有無諗過一個人如果做咗植物人十一年<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係十一年</span><br />\n<br />\n就算俾你奇跡身體變返正常 你心理會有幾大創傷<br />\n<br />\n如果佢真係好似佢老母講咁有意識<br />\n<br />\n有無諗過佢呢十一年每日有幾痛苦<br />\n<br />\n根本返唔到轉頭<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢老母試下做一年植物人 睇下仲淨返 d 乜野"},{"pid":"3e37c7538103cf4b7c5f76865f187bd1b32adf87","tid":1164551,"uid":72939,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"e97e1e3ba2e28bf7dad3608318e6b788795178d0","tid":1164551,"uid":238214,"like":8,"dislike":45,"score":-37,"quote":{"pid":"eb8cc5cbf92ab9848af205d78274827501b10037","tid":1164551,"uid":16061,"like":789,"dislike":39,"score":750,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T07:43:24.000Z","msg":"有無人覺得老婆比父母更有權去決定"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T10:15:54.000Z","msg":"不同意 父母只得2個。 老婆可以無上限"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T12:45:57.000Z","msg":"做你老婆真係喊三聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8323045008d32dc79519214b68a6245526a86e1","tid":1164551,"uid":10890,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"1a0bf4495a28843cad7c54ac58f5838bd475dec2","tid":1164551,"uid":143033,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T07:47:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T12:46:50.000Z","msg":"Medical Ethics有樣嘢叫Doctrine of double effects:<br />\n&ldquo;if doing something morally good has a morally bad side-effect it's ethically OK to do it providing the bad side-effect wasn't intended. This is true even if you foresaw that the bad effect would probably happen.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n用Morphine/嗎啡就係一個好例子<br />\n用Morphine可以幫病人鎮痛<br />\n但用得太多會抑制病人嘅CNS至死<br />\n如果有個末期病人係極度痛但又已經藥石無靈<br />\n幫佢鎮痛係一個morally good嘅intention<br />\n所以就算用morphine用到佢死<br />\n你都唔算morally wrong<br />\n因為你唔係想佢死<br />\n你只係想佢冇咁痛<br />\n雖然冇咁痛嘅過程會令佢死"},{"pid":"18160fb7524e0dfeb0a62d51da8e202a3a4a73bc","tid":1164551,"uid":10890,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"8266965d4b5ec4d0d69d910e54e45771a12537fa","tid":1164551,"uid":38007,"like":225,"dislike":1,"score":224,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T08:14:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">「慢慢餓死及渴死」</span><br />\n支持有安樂死呢樣野<br />\n但係呢「慢慢餓死及渴死」絶對唔支持"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T12:52:59.000Z","msg":"法國唔容許安樂死<br />\n當地醫生唔可以以「令病人死」嘅意圖去做任何嘢<br />\n佢地可以基於「用維生機器令佢痛苦而且睇唔出有治療效果」呢個意圖嚟withdraw life support<br />\n或者「希望病人冇咁痛」嚟用大量Morphine<br />\n<br />\n但唔可以一針啪落去令病人死<br />\n因為咁樣你個意圖就係「要病人死」"},{"pid":"918b6d6f68d948e377e97b52369ed49cd5b04621","tid":1164551,"uid":120423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T12:57:04.000Z","msg":"生不如死 <br />\n真係好辛苦<br />\n支持安樂死呢樣野！"},{"pid":"f8647352453900f1723edfc422358a4ac127b1b3","tid":1164551,"uid":92663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T12:59:37.000Z","msg":"諗起乙一個本失去的世界<br />\n訓係到但係咩都做唔到真係好恐怖<br />\n快手死咗佢算"},{"pid":"fd044d65385b3dfc84b8f963b68a397decc0a990","tid":1164551,"uid":55177,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c2c4291eee7a4999327d1791878cbddc760f29dc","tid":1164551,"uid":201604,"like":478,"dislike":6,"score":472,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T07:44:49.000Z","msg":"咩父母會想自己個仔繼續受苦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T13:07:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7ebea4b5274d47c28f3cf31d0f31f14962e26bc","tid":1164551,"uid":239033,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"db08a37702773eb3420c35a1ac9c6f5ee62f94f7","tid":1164551,"uid":72902,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"4b314bb50e9093d0f6f660ef53cd3a2135240c6a","tid":1164551,"uid":141151,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"bca9436c